== 製作 ==
===开发===
2007年2月初，[[鲁伯特·默多克|鲁伯特·默多克]]宣布巴隆·科恩已经与《波拉特》的发行商[[二十世纪福斯|二十世纪福斯]]签订续集合约<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/topNews/idUKN0820626120070208 |title=Sacha Baron Cohen signs for ''Borat 2'' |access-date=2020-09-26 |last=Li |first=Kenneth |work=Reuters |date=2007-02-09 |archive-date=2007-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071225082721/http://uk.reuters.com/article/topNews/idUKN0820626120070208 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴隆·科恩后来宣布续集取消，因为自己已经不太知道如何在影片和《{{tsl|en|Da Ali G Show|阿里·G个人秀}}》中避免被人发现<ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://variety.com/2007/film/news/baron-cohen-retires-borat-ali-g-1117978095/ |title=Baron Cohen retires Borat, Ali G |magazine=Variety |date=2007-12-21 |access-date=2020-09-27 |agency=Associated Press |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026225134/https://variety.com/2007/film/news/baron-cohen-retires-borat-ali-g-1117978095/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。福斯发言人随后表示续集规划为时尚早，但对续集的构思持开放意见<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/film/borat-sequel-put-on-hold/2007/02/09/1170524280667.html |title=Borat Sequel Put on Hold |newspaper=The Age |agency=Reuters |access-date=2020-09-27 |date=2007-02-09 |archive-date=2007-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070212135352/http://www.theage.com.au/news/film/borat-sequel-put-on-hold/2007/02/09/1170524280667.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年，巴隆·科恩在{{tsl|en|FXX|FXX}}系列节目《Ali G: Rezurection》中再度扮演波拉特，该节目收录了《阿里·G个人秀》的小品，有新画面出现<ref>{{cite news |first=David S. |last=Morgan |url=http://www.showbuzz.cbsnews.com/stories/2007/12/22/movies/main3641923.shtml |title=Borat He Dead, I Kill Him, Gone |work=CBS News |date=2007-12-22 |access-date=2009-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071229064415/http://www.showbuzz.cbsnews.com/stories/2007/12/22/movies/main3641923.shtml |archive-date=2007-12-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2015年，巴隆·科恩在《[[吉米·坎摩尔直播秀|吉米·坎摩尔直播秀]]》宣传电影《[[特務大臨演|特務大臨演]]》，曾短暂扮演波拉特<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.vulture.com/2015/12/borat-jimmy-kimmel-live-brothers-grimsby.html |date=2015-12-10 |website=Vulture |access-date=2020-09-27 |title=Borat Dropped by ''Jimmy Kimmel Live'' to Bash Donald Trump, Anti-Promote Sacha Baron Cohen's Latest Movie |last=Fitz-Gerald |first=Sean |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027175533/https://www.vulture.com/2015/12/borat-jimmy-kimmel-live-brothers-grimsby.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年11月，他再度化身波拉特，鼓励美国人在当年的[[2018年美国中期选举|中期选举]]踊跃投票<ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/borat-jimmy-kimmel-live-midterms-1203021791/ |date=2018-11-06 |magazine=Variety |access-date=2020-09-27 |title=Borat Gets Out the Vote for 'Premier' Trump on ''Jimmy Kimmel Live!'' |last=Nyren |first=Erin |archive-date=2020-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001120807/https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/borat-jimmy-kimmel-live-midterms-1203021791/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片上映两年前，巴隆·科恩在政界异常活跃，多次在演讲和专访中宣扬对抗种族主义。他坚持续集会在[[2020年美国总统选举|2020年美国总统选举]]前夕发行，让美国人警惕社会正沦为[[不自由的民主|不自由的民主]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/17/style/sacha-baron-cohen-maureen-dowd-interview.html |title=Sacha Baron Cohen: This Time He's Serious |date=2020-10-17 |access-date=2020-10-17 |newspaper=The New York Times |last=Dowd |first=Maureen |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017091411/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/17/style/sacha-baron-cohen-maureen-dowd-interview.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

和巴隆·科恩的其他电影一样，影片配乐由哥哥{{tsl|en|Erran Baron Cohen|艾伦·巴隆·科恩}}负责，其他原创配乐包括罗马尼亚巴尔干乐队{{tsl|en|Fanfare Ciocărlia|Fanfare Ciocărlia}}负责，他们翻唱了《Just the Two of Us》。加拿大原生态音乐人阿德里安·拉索（Adrian Raso）表演了《Urn St. Tavern》<ref>{{Cite web |publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |access-date=2020-10-28 |date=2020-10-28 |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/kitchener-waterloo/guelph-guitarist-adrian-raso-urn-st-tavern-borat-movie-1.5780024 |last=Brown |first=Desmond |title=Guitarist Shares 'Surreal' Experience of Song Used in New Borat Movie |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029112444/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/kitchener-waterloo/guelph-guitarist-adrian-raso-urn-st-tavern-borat-movie-1.5780024 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

