拍摄工作随着图拉一角的选角工作完成，而正式展开。巴卡洛娃在600名参与试镜的演员中脱颖而出，担纲图拉这一角色<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/10/maria-bakalova-borat-2-oscars-1234595322/ |title=Maria Bakalova for Oscars? Sacha Baron Cohen Says It's a 'Travesty' If Academy Snubs ''Borat 2'' Star |date=2020-10-26 |access-date=2020-10-27 |last=Sharf |first=Zack |website=TheWrap |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031221330/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/10/maria-bakalova-borat-2-oscars-1234595322/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴卡洛娃最初得知自己是在为一部未具名的好莱坞电影发去自己表演的视频，怀疑是[[人口贩卖|人口贩卖]]骗局，但她最终去了伦敦，和巴隆·科恩一起排练，证明这是个真正的表演机会<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/11/movies/maria-bakalova-borat.html |title=Meet Maria Bakalova, the Breakout Star of the ''Borat'' Sequel |last=Itzkoff |first=Dave |date=2020-11-11 |access-date=2020-11-12 |work=The New York Times |archive-date=2020-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201226213205/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/11/movies/maria-bakalova-borat.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片早期的一个恶作剧是在[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[阿灵顿_(得克萨斯州)|阿灵顿]]的[[練習場_(高爾夫球)|高尔夫练习场]]采访{{tsl|en|Texas Agriculture Commissioner|得克萨斯州农业专员}}{{tsl|en|Sid Miller (politician)|席德·米勒}}，于2019年末拍摄完成，但后来在成片中被删除，只出现在预告片中<ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://golf.com/news/the-borat-golf-scene-that-was-left-on-the-editing-room-floor/ |title=The Borat Golf Scene that Was Left on the Editing-Room Floor |magazine=Golf Magazine |last=Sens |first=Josh |date=2020-10-23 |access-date=2020-10-23 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026103418/https://golf.com/news/the-borat-golf-scene-that-was-left-on-the-editing-room-floor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年2月，巴隆·科恩打扮成[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]，闯入[[保守政治行動會議|保守政治行動會議]]，不过当时他的真实身份未被揭露<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/trump-impersonator-interrupts-vice-president-mike-pences-cpac/story?id=69261891 |title=Trump Impersonator Interrupts Vice President Mike Pence's CPAC Speech |work=ABC News |last=Stoddart |first=Michelle |date=2020-02-27 |access-date=2020-10-01 |archive-date=2020-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001183629/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/trump-impersonator-interrupts-vice-president-mike-pences-cpac/story?id=69261891 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |access-date=2020-10-01 |url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/sacha-baron-cohen-pranks-mike-pence-as-trump-in-borat-2-trailer |title=Sacha Baron Cohen Pranks Mike Pence as Trump in ''Borat 2'' Trailer |first=Matt |last=Wilstein |date=2020-10-01 |work=The Daily Beast |archive-date=2020-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001180151/https://www.thedailybeast.com/sacha-baron-cohen-pranks-mike-pence-as-trump-in-borat-2-trailer |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://ijr.org/protestor-escorted-out-cpac-dressed-trump/ |last=Ellis |first=Meghan |date=2020-02-27 |access-date=2020-10-28 |work=Independent Journal Review |title=Protestor Escorted out of CPAC for Shouting at Pence While Dressed Up as Trump |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101040528/https://ijr.org/protestor-escorted-out-cpac-dressed-trump/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

同月，巴隆·科恩前往[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]][[梅肯_(乔治亚州)|梅肯]]，在一场假的{{tsl|en|debutante ball|处女舞会}}，戏弄到场人士<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ajc.com/life/radiotvtalk-blog/macon-residents-pranked-by-sacha-baron-cohen-for-his-borat-2-film/3FURBPCUQBCHHNBEWG62GEJVTY/ |date=2020-10-05 |access-date=2020-10-06 |last=Ho |first=Rodney |work=Atlanta Journal-Constitution |title=Macon Residents Pranked by Sacha Baron Cohen for His ''Borat 2'' Film |archive-date=2020-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007000238/https://www.ajc.com/life/radiotvtalk-blog/macon-residents-pranked-by-sacha-baron-cohen-for-his-borat-2-film/3FURBPCUQBCHHNBEWG62GEJVTY/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他向{{tsl|en|Johnston–Felton–Hay House|约翰斯顿-费尔顿-海伊之家}}的活动主办方谎称自己在拍一部[[成年礼|成长题材]]电影<ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/10/borat-2-sequel-spoilers |title=''Borat 2'' Spoilers: How Sacha Baron Cohen Pulled Off His Biggest Stunts |last=Rosen |first=Christopher |date=2020-10-23 |access-date=2020-10-23 |magazine=Vanity Fair |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025084339/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/10/borat-2-sequel-spoilers |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他安排巴卡洛娃在他开场的时候坐在车顶，被当地警方截停。警方随身记录仪显然巴隆·科恩当时称自己是喜剧演员，正在演戏<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fox5atlanta.com/video/864824 |title=Borat Traffic Stop in Georgia |publisher=WAGA-TV |date=2020-10-27 |access-date=2020-10-28 |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110080115/https://www.fox5atlanta.com/video/864824 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后剧组来到[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]][[玛丽埃塔_(佐治亚州)|玛丽埃塔]]的科尔·艾美犹太教堂（Temple Kol Emeth），拍摄和埃文斯的戏份<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.vulture.com/article/whos-who-in-borat-2-a-guide-to-every-notable-cameo.html |date=2020-10-28 |website=Vulture |access-date=2020-10-28 |title=Who's Who in ''Borat 2'': A Guide to Every Notable Cameo |last=Reilly |first=Dan |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028134738/https://www.vulture.com/article/whos-who-in-borat-2-a-guide-to-every-notable-cameo.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。剧组至少两次前往南卡罗来纳州北部，在面包店、紧急怀孕中心和万圣节用品店拍摄<ref>{{Cite news |date=2020-10-03 |access-date=2020-10-28 |last=Cary |first=Nathaniel |newspaper=The Post and Courier |title=Borat Sequel with Sasha Baron Cohen Quietly Filmed in Upstate with Unsuspecting Marks |url=https://www.postandcourier.com/greenville/business/borat-sequel-with-sasha-baron-cohen-quietly-filmed-in-upstate-with-unsuspecting-marks/article_73c8e9fe-04f3-11eb-96bf-f35b6db1bdf2.html |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027041520/https://www.postandcourier.com/greenville/business/borat-sequel-with-sasha-baron-cohen-quietly-filmed-in-upstate-with-unsuspecting-marks/article_73c8e9fe-04f3-11eb-96bf-f35b6db1bdf2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年6月底，科恩在[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]][[奥林匹亚_(华盛顿州)|奥林匹亚]]上演[[恶作剧|恶作剧]]<ref>{{Cite news |newspaper=The Olympian |url=https://www.theolympian.com/news/local/article243834242.html |title=Did Comedian Sacha Baron Cohen Crash Rally in Downtown Olympia? |last=Boone |first=Rolf |date=2020-07-27 |access-date=2020-09-27}}</ref>，率领现场人数合唱一首原创种族主义歌曲<ref name="racist">{{Cite magazine |url=https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/sacha-baron-cohen-prank-rally-who-is-america-1234692557/ |title=Sacha Baron Cohen Pranks Conservative Rally into Singing Racist Lyrics |last=Moreau |first=Jordan |date=2020-06-28 |access-date=2020-09-27 |magazine=Variety |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929032336/https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/sacha-baron-cohen-prank-rally-who-is-america-1234692557/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，还采访了在场人士<ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/06/sacha-baron-cohen-trolls-alt-right-rally-with-racist-sing-along |title=Sacha Baron Cohen Trolls Far-Right Rally with Racist Sing-Along |last=Hoffman |first=Jordan |date=2020-06-28 |access-date=2020-09-27 |magazine=Vanity Fair |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031235844/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/06/sacha-baron-cohen-trolls-alt-right-rally-with-racist-sing-along |dead-url=no }}</ref>。负责纠察的示威者认出巴隆·科恩，开怀大笑，让观众和主办方意识到他们被捉弄，准备采用暴力手段冲向舞台，结果被剧组雇佣的安保人员挡住。最终巴隆·科恩和剧组成员被迫逃进一辆私人救护车，只身抵住车门，反正示威者闯入<ref>{{cite episode |title=Sacha Baron Cohen, Jeff Tweedy |series=The Late Show with Stephen Colbert |last=Colbert |first=Stephen |url=https://www.cbs.com/shows/the-late-show-with-stephen-colbert/video/x3eb5Ugihg2JIKxr2TQ5Tf_or3DVSQy2/the-late-show-10-26-20-sacha-baron-cohen-jeff-tweedy-/ |network=CBS All Access |season=6 |number=24 |access-date=2020-11-10 |date=2020-10-26 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031224832/https://www.cbs.com/shows/the-late-show-with-stephen-colbert/video/x3eb5Ugihg2JIKxr2TQ5Tf_or3DVSQy2/the-late-show-10-26-20-sacha-baron-cohen-jeff-tweedy-/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。新闻媒体很快便了解到恶搞事件，但猜测这是新一季《{{tsl|en|Who Is America?|谁是美国？}}》的内容<ref name="racist" />。2020年7月，巴隆·科恩给[[魯迪·朱利安尼|魯迪·朱利安尼]]安排一场假采访，在采访期间穿着粉色比基尼闯入，促使朱利安尼当场报警<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://pagesix.com/2020/07/08/rudy-giuliani-called-the-nypd-on-sacha-baron-cohen-over-prank-interview/ |title=Rudy Giuliani Called the NYPD on Sacha Baron Cohen over Prank Interview |work=Page Six |date=2020-07-08 |access-date=2020-09-27 |last1=Smith |first1=Emily |last2=Siegler |first2=Mara |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927165538/https://pagesix.com/2020/07/08/rudy-giuliani-called-the-nypd-on-sacha-baron-cohen-over-prank-interview/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

次月，巴隆·科恩被发现打扮成波拉特在洛杉矶拍戏，外界猜测他的下一个项目是《波拉特》续集<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/sacha-baron-cohen-borat-sequel-filming-who-america-a9678111.html |title=Sacha Baron Cohen Spotted Reprising Borat Role in Possible Sequel to 2006 film |last=White |first=Adam |date=2020-08-19 |access-date=2020-09-27 |newspaper=The Independent |archive-date=2020-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201014162123/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/sacha-baron-cohen-borat-sequel-filming-who-america-a9678111.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。拍戏的两天中，巴隆·科恩需要穿着防弹衣以防万一<ref name="amazon">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2020/09/borat-sequel-release-date-sacha-baron-cohen-amazon-prime-presidential-election-1234587077/ |title=''Borat'' Sequel Acquired by Amazon Studios; Sacha Baron Cohen Film Will Bow on Prime Video Right Before Election Day |work=Deadline Hollywood |first=Mike |last=Fleming Jr. |date=2020-09-29 |access-date=2020-09-29 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929210227/https://deadline.com/2020/09/borat-sequel-release-date-sacha-baron-cohen-amazon-prime-presidential-election-1234587077/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年9月，传闻指影片已经完成拍摄和剪辑，正交由电影行政部门审阅<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://collider.com/borat-2-sequel-sacha-baron-cohen/ |title=Exclusive: ''Borat 2'' Has Already Been Shot and Screened by Sacha Baron Cohen |last=Sneider |first=Jeff |date=2020-09-08 |access-date=2020-09-27 |publisher=Collider |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929065226/https://collider.com/borat-2-sequel-sacha-baron-cohen/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片原名《波拉特2：大成功》（''Borat 2: Great Success''），后改为《波拉特：为最近名声不好的哈萨克斯坦国向副总统迈克尔·彭斯供奉色情猴子》（''Borat: Gift of Pornographic Monkey to Vice Premiere Mikhael Pence to Make Benefit Recently Diminished Nation of Kazakhstan''），其中后者被其中一版标题画面采用。9月20日，潜入[[白宫|白宫]]的巴卡洛娃接受[[同一个美国新闻网|同一个美国新闻网]]记者{{tsl|en|Chanel Rion|香奈儿·里昂}}采访，但该片段在成片中被删除<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/borats-daughter-visited-white-house-came-within-meters-of-trump-met-his-son/ |title='Borat's Daughter' Visited White House, Came Within Meters of Trump, Met His Son |newspaper=The Times of Israel |date=2020-10-24 |access-date=2020-10-27 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027114717/https://www.timesofisrael.com/borats-daughter-visited-white-house-came-within-meters-of-trump-met-his-son/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。哈萨克斯坦乡下的戏份在[[罗马尼亚|罗马尼亚]]取景，但由于前作取景地的村民感到不满，本作换了一个村子。戏份中有当地演员受雇出演<ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/10/borat-2-subsequent-moviefilm-sacha-baron-cohen-review |title=''Borat Subsequent Moviefilm'' Brings Back Borat, with His Daughter in Tow |last=Saraiya |first=Sonia |date=2020-10-21 |access-date=2020-10-23 |magazine=Vanity Fair |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021192824/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/10/borat-2-subsequent-moviefilm-sacha-baron-cohen-review |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

影片采用72台序列号不同的摄影机拍摄，包括高端电影摄影机及智能手机。制作团队采用简单的编码器，复刻早期电影的观感。影片的A、B、C镜头为[[ARRI|ARRI]] Amira和[[阿萊Alexa|ALEXA]] Mini，与隐藏小镜头、机械臂、低端应用甚至iPhone搭配使用<ref>{{Cite web|last=Mendelovich|first=Yossy|date=2021-03-02|title=Borat 2 Cinematography: ARRI Amiras, ALEXA Minis, iPhones, and Much More|url=https://ymcinema.com/2021/03/02/borat-2-cinematography-arri-amiras-alexa-minis-iphones-and-much-more/|access-date=2021-03-02|website=Y.M.Cinema - News & Insights on Digital Cinema|archive-date=2021-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110013504/https://ymcinema.com/2021/03/02/borat-2-cinematography-arri-amiras-alexa-minis-iphones-and-much-more/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《芭樂特電影續集》定於2020年10月23日在[[亞馬遜影片|亞馬遜影片]]播出<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://collider.com/borat-2-amazon-prime-video-release-date/ |date=2020-09-29 |accessdate=2020-09-29 |title=''Borat 2'' to Premiere on Amazon Prime Video in October, Timed to Election Day |last=Sneider |first=Jeff |publisher=Collider |archive-date=2020-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002044244/https://collider.com/borat-2-amazon-prime-video-release-date/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2020/09/borat-sequel-release-date-sacha-baron-cohen-amazon-prime-presidential-election-1234587077/ |title=''Borat'' Sequel Acquired by Amazon Studios; Sacha Baron Cohen Film Will Bow on Prime Video Right Before Election Day |work=Deadline Hollywood |first=Mike |last=Fleming, Jr |date=2020-09-29 |accessdate=2020-09-29 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929210227/https://deadline.com/2020/09/borat-sequel-release-date-sacha-baron-cohen-amazon-prime-presidential-election-1234587077/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年10月1日，發佈首支預告片<ref>{{cite web |last1=Earl |first1=William |title=''Borat Subsequent Moviefilm'' Trailer: Sacha Baron Cohen Takes on Coronavirus and Pence |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/borat-subsequent-moviefilm-trailer-coronavirus-trump-1234788855/ |accessdate=2020-10-01 |work=Variety |date=2020-10-01 |archive-date=2020-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001164223/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/borat-subsequent-moviefilm-trailer-coronavirus-trump-1234788855/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片上线首周末，[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]未公布准确的收看人数，只透露全球观众达数千万。{{tsl|en|Samba TV|Samba TV}}表示美国收看人数达160万，其中10月22日点映4.5万，不过亚马逊表示这些数字不准确<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2020/digital/news/borat-2-viewership-numbers-amazon-opening-weekend-mulan-1234816491/ |work=Variety |date=2020-10-27 |access-date=2020-10-27 |last=Spangler |first=Todd |title='' Borat 2'' Drew 'Tens of Millions' of Viewers Over Opening Weekend, Amazon Says |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027152813/https://variety.com/2020/digital/news/borat-2-viewership-numbers-amazon-opening-weekend-mulan-1234816491/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。MarketCast追踪影片发行前后在[[社交媒体|社交媒体]]上被提及110万次<ref>{{Cite web |work=Fast Company |date=2020-11-02 |access-date=2020-11-03 |title=How Amazon's ''Borat{{nbsp}}2'' Reveals the New Playbook for the Streaming Movie Blockbuster |url=https://www.fastcompany.com/90569725/how-amazons-borat-2-reveals-the-new-playbook-for-the-streaming-movie-blockbuster |last=Laporte |first=Nicole |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102234055/https://www.fastcompany.com/90569725/how-amazons-borat-2-reveals-the-new-playbook-for-the-streaming-movie-blockbuster |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[尼爾森收視率|尼爾森收視率]]将影片列入10月19日一周收视榜第八位，总观看时长达5.7亿分钟，相当于590万次观看<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/borat-2-debuts-in-nielsens-streaming-top-10 |date=2020-11-19 |access-date=2020-11-19 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |title=''Borat 2'' Debuts in Nielsen's Streaming Top 10 |last=Porter |first=Rick |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119183135/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/borat-2-debuts-in-nielsens-streaming-top-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月，《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》指影片是当年迄今为止观看人数最多的流媒体直接发行作品<ref>{{cite web |last=Bridge |first=Gavin |date=2020-11-04 |url=https://variety.com/vip/data-borat-2-second-only-to-hamilton-in-most-watched-u-s-svod-movies-of-2020-1234823177/ |title=''Borat 2'' Second Only to ''Hamilton'' in Most-Watched U.S. SVOD Movies of 2020 |work=Variety |access-date=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2020-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104174256/https://variety.com/vip/data-borat-2-second-only-to-hamilton-in-most-watched-u-s-svod-movies-of-2020-1234823177/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]收录295条评论，打出85%的新鲜度，平均得分7.2/10。网站共识写道：“《波拉特续集》证明沙查·巴隆·科恩的喜剧创作仍是一把锋利的工具，暴露出美国文化最被误导、最令人彻底反感的角落<ref name="rt">{{cite web |title=''Borat: Subsequent Moviefilm'' (2020) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/borat_subsequent_moviefilm |website=Rotten Tomatoes |access-date=2020-11-04 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101010337/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/borat_subsequent_moviefilm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]收录49条评论，打出68/100的平均分<ref name="rt" />。多数媒体给予影片普遍正面的评价，尽管[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]和[[路透社|路透社]]认为影片的评价“褒贬不一”<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-54642496 |title=''Borat Subsequent Moviefilm'': Mixed Reviews for Sacha Baron Cohen Sequel |work=BBC News |date=2020-10-22 |access-date=2020-10-22 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022111350/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-54642496 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |publisher=Reuters |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/film-borat-2/borat-bounces-back-just-ahead-of-u-s-elections-idUSL1N2HC1OG |title=Borat Bounces Back Just Ahead of U.S. Elections |date=2020-10-21 |access-date=2020-10-22 |first=Jill |last=Serjeant |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027161057/https://www.reuters.com/article/film-borat-2/borat-bounces-back-just-ahead-of-u-s-elections-idUSL1N2HC1OG |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 轶事 ==
=== 朱利安尼的出现 ===
影片中，鲁迪·朱利安尼面对假扮记者的女演员玛丽亚·巴卡洛娃，把手伸进裤子的一幕引发争议。在酒店客房接受完采访，两人回到睡房，巴卡洛娃帮朱利安尼摘掉身上的麦克风，而当时喝了酒的朱利安尼问巴卡洛娃要住址和电话号码，过程中还脱去上衣。这时巴隆·科恩充进房间，大喊“她才15岁，对你来说太老了”<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/oct/21/borat-subsequent-moviefilm-review-sacha-baron-cohen-trump |title=''Borat Subsequent Moviefilm'' Review– Cinema's Top Troll Goes Baiting in Trump's US |last=Bradshaw |first=Peter |date=2020-10-21 |access-date=2020-10-21 |newspaper=The Guardian |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021193604/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/oct/21/borat-subsequent-moviefilm-review-sacha-baron-cohen-trump |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.npr.org/2020/10/22/926593980/borat-sequel-grabs-a-political-news-cycle-at-least-momentarily |title=''Borat'' Sequel Grabs a Political News Cycle—At Least Momentarily |last=Tsioulcas |first=Anastasia |publisher=NPR |date=2020-10-22 |access-date=2020-10-22 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022180928/https://www.npr.org/2020/10/22/926593980/borat-sequel-grabs-a-political-news-cycle-at-least-momentarily |dead-url=no }}</ref>。朱利安尼否认图谋不轨，认为这些指控是在污蔑拜登之子[[亨特·拜登|亨特·拜登]]邮件门事件，但实际上有关场景是在邮件门几个月前拍摄<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/rudy-giuliani-claims-borat-hit-job-is-retaliation-for-hunter-biden-attack/ |work=The Daily Beast |date=2020-10-21 |access-date=2020-10-21 |last=Wilstein |first=Matt |title=Rudy Giuliani Claims Borat 'Hit Job' Is Retaliation for Hunter Biden Attack |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023204737/https://www.thedailybeast.com/rudy-giuliani-claims-borat-hit-job-is-retaliation-for-hunter-biden-attack |dead-url=no }}</ref>。相关戏份的争议促使巴隆·科恩打扮成波拉特，录了一条短片回应朱利安尼<ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://slate.com/culture/2020/10/borat-giuliani-sacha-baron-cohen-video-analyzed.html |magazine=Slate |date=2020-10-22 |access-date=2020-10-22 |title=A Shot-by-Shot Analysis of the New ''Borat''{{'}}s Giuliani Scene |last=Dessem |first=Matthew |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023030605/https://slate.com/culture/2020/10/borat-giuliani-sacha-baron-cohen-video-analyzed.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在《[[早安美国|早安美国]]》采访中，脱离角色的巴隆·科恩为该戏份站台，表示“事实就是这样。他就是做了这样的事情”<ref>{{cite web |last=Blackwelder |first=Carson |title=Sacha Baron Cohen Responds to ''Borat 2'' Scene with Rudy Giuliani: 'He Did What He Did' |url=https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/culture/story/sacha-baron-cohen-responds-borat-scene-rudy-giuliani-73783279 |work=Good Morning America |date=2020-10-24 |access-date=2020-10-24 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024005232/https://www.goodmorningamerica.com/culture/story/sacha-baron-cohen-responds-borat-scene-rudy-giuliani-73783279 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在竞选活动中，[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]称巴隆·科恩不搞笑，是“变态”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-joe-biden-donald-trump-elections-campaigns-983f1a333b3acd4d5a6311254fb594ef |title=The Latest: Trump calls 'Borat' star an unfunny 'creep' |publisher=Associated Press |date=2020-10-24 |access-date=2020-10-24 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027175533/https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-joe-biden-donald-trump-elections-campaigns-983f1a333b3acd4d5a6311254fb594ef |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴隆感谢特朗普免费帮他宣传，说自己“也不觉得特朗普总统幽默”<ref name="thanks">{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sacha-baron-cohen-responds-to-criticism-from-trump-i-dont-find-you-funny-either |title=Sacha Baron Cohen Responds to Criticism from Trump: 'I Don't Find You Funny Either' |last=Beresford |first=Trilby |date=2020-10-24 |access-date=2020-10-24 |magazine=The Hollywood Reporter |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024194136/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sacha-baron-cohen-responds-to-criticism-from-trump-i-dont-find-you-funny-either |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后朱利安尼在多家媒体上参与辩论，其中[[福斯新闻频道|福斯新闻频道]]记者{{le|肯尼迪 (评论员)|Kennedy (commentator)|肯尼迪}}就相关戏份及拜登邮件的真实性，与他对质<ref name="gross">{{Cite web |url=https://www.newsweek.com/rudy-giuliani-kennedy-fox-borat-richard-steele-1542790 |title=Fox's Kennedy Tells Rudy Giuliani She Was 'Grossed Out' by ''Borat 2'' Scene in Tense Interview |last=Nolan |first=Emma |work=Newsweek |date=2020-10-28 |access-date=2020-10-28 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028151128/https://www.newsweek.com/rudy-giuliani-kennedy-fox-borat-richard-steele-1542790 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后，巴伦嘲笑朱利安尼在特朗普败选后于{{le|四季景观工程公司记者发布会|Four Seasons Total Landscaping press conference|四季景观工程公司}}举行新闻发布会<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.newsweek.com/sacha-baron-cohen-pokes-fun-rudy-giuliani-following-attorneys-press-conference-convicted-sex-1546164 |work=Newsweek |date=2020-11-09 |access-date=2020-11-10 |title=Sacha Baron Cohen Pokes Fun at Rudy Giuliani Following Attorney's Press Conference with Convicted Sex Offender |last=Roos |first=Meghan |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110080113/https://www.newsweek.com/sacha-baron-cohen-pokes-fun-rudy-giuliani-following-attorneys-press-conference-convicted-sex-1546164 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同时取消早前为败选的特朗普提供的工作机会<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-11-09/trump-election-sacha-baron-cohen-tweet-borat |last=Carras |first=Christi |work=The Los Angeles Times |date=2020-11-09 |access-date=2020-11-10 |title=Sacha Baron Cohen: Sorry, Trump, No Film Role for You After Election Loss |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109225043/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-11-09/trump-election-sacha-baron-cohen-tweet-borat |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 不公平对待的指控 ===
{{quote box
| width = 30%|“尽管这部电影很有趣，但大多数哈萨克人不理解波拉特的幽默......至少大家（看完会）查找地图，看下它到底是不是真的国家，但这其中也有一些负面的效果。我一个住在美国的朋友告诉我，说在美的哈萨克人开始遭受欺凌。”|——哈萨克斯坦讽刺作家穆拉特·迪尔马诺夫（Murat Dilmanov）评《波拉特》在哈萨克斯坦造成的反应，以及国际社会对他祖国的关注<ref>{{Cite web |work=The Washington Post |date=2020-11-05 |access-date=2020-11-10 |last=Khurshudyan |first=Isabelle |title=We Asked Kazakh Celebrities What They Think of ''Borat''. The verdict was less than 'very nice'. |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/borat-kazakhstan-reviews-movie/2020/11/05/902646e6-1849-11eb-8bda-814ca56e138b_story.html |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108004834/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/borat-kazakhstan-reviews-movie/2020/11/05/902646e6-1849-11eb-8bda-814ca56e138b_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}
影片制作者因在片中展现对{{tsl|en|Holocaust survivors|犹太人大屠杀幸存者}}茱蒂丝·蒂姆·伊万斯（Judith Dim Evans）的采访，面临[[诈骗|诈骗]]官司。伊万斯在影片上映前不久去世，她的后人发起诉讼，声称她不满意自己的形象在影片中被用作商业用途<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.ajc.com/life/radiotvtalk-blog/estate-of-late-holocaust-survivor-sues-creators-of-borat-over-appearance-in-upcoming-sequel/B7Y2IK2F5NA3TFP2B6GEGKQHTI/ |date=2020-10-13 |access-date=2020-10-14 |last=Ho |first=Rodney |newspaper=The Atlanta Journal-Constitution |title=Estate of Late Holocaust Survivor Sues Creators of ''Borat'' Over Appearance in Upcoming Sequel |archive-date=2020-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015061335/https://www.ajc.com/life/radiotvtalk-blog/estate-of-late-holocaust-survivor-sues-creators-of-borat-over-appearance-in-upcoming-sequel/B7Y2IK2F5NA3TFP2B6GEGKQHTI/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Lewis |first=Isobel |date=2020-10-15 |access-date=2020-10-16 |title=Borat Creators Sued by Estate of Late Holocaust Survivor Who Claimed She Thought Film Was Real Documentary |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/borat-2-holocaust-survivor-judith-dim-evans-sacha-baron-cohen-b1042505.html |newspaper=The Independent |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029000317/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/borat-2-holocaust-survivor-judith-dim-evans-sacha-baron-cohen-b1042505.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴隆·科恩在影片中致敬了伊万斯，称自己曾{{le|脱离角色|broke character}}，向伊万斯表示那个段落是个噱头，目的是释除她对波拉特的反犹太人言论的担忧<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2020/10/sacha-baron-cohen-borat-sequel-combat-holocaust-deniai-sites-facebook-twitter-evolving-lawsuit-1234598201/ |work=Deadline Hollywood |access-date=2020-10-16 |date=2020-10-15 |title=How Sacha Baron Cohen's Plan to Use ''Borat'' Sequel to Combat Facebook & Twitter Holocaust Denier Policies Evolved with Abrupt About Face & Surprise Lawsuit |last=Fleming Jr. |first=Mike |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017075407/https://deadline.com/2020/10/sacha-baron-cohen-borat-sequel-combat-holocaust-deniai-sites-facebook-twitter-evolving-lawsuit-1234598201/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。官司于10月26日撤销<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thewrap.com/borat-sequel-lawsuit-filed-by-holocaust-survivors-estate-dismissed/ |title=''Borat'' Sequel Lawsuit Filed by Holocaust Survivor's Estate Dismissed |date=2020-10-26 |access-date=2020-10-26 |last=Welk |first=Brian |website=TheWrap |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027020427/https://www.thewrap.com/borat-sequel-lawsuit-filed-by-holocaust-survivors-estate-dismissed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在片中出现的保姆珍妮丝·琼斯（Jeanise Jones）觉得被剧组“背叛”。她告诉《[[纽约邮报|纽约邮报]]》，剧组一开始说她参与的纪录片是讲少女为嫁给老男人做准备<ref>{{cite news |last=Zornosa |first=Laura |title=''Borat'' Babysitter Didn't Know the Film Was Satire but Doesn't feel 'Betrayed' |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-10-27/borat-babysitter-had-no-idea-the-film-was-satire-feels-betrayed |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |access-date=2020-10-30 |date=2020-10-29 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029115207/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-10-27/borat-babysitter-had-no-idea-the-film-was-satire-feels-betrayed |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但直到影片发行前，她才了解到作品的本质<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://bleedingcool.com/movies/borat-2s-unwitting-star-jeanise-jones-talks-to-bleeding-cool/ |last=Johnston |first=Rich |title=''Borat 2''{{'}}s Unwitting Star Jeanise Jones Talks to Bleeding Cool |publisher=Bleeding Cool |date=2020-11-13 |access-date=2020-11-13 |dead-url=no |archive-date=2020-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201226213240/https://bleedingcool.com/movies/borat-2s-unwitting-star-jeanise-jones-talks-to-bleeding-cool/ }}</ref>。不过她后来收回言论，说没有生剧组的气<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://oklahoman.com/article/5674862/oklahoma-woman-called-moral-compass-of-new-borat-2-movie |work=The Oklahoman |last=Hinton |first=Carla |date=2020-10-27 |access-date=2020-10-27 |title='They Loved Her': Meet Oklahoma's Jeanise Jones, the 'Moral Compass' and Breakout Star of ''Borat 2'' |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027185206/https://oklahoman.com/article/5674862/oklahoma-woman-called-moral-compass-of-new-borat-2-movie |dead-url=no }}</ref>，全怪自己没有读发行文件<ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/borat-2-babysitter-sacha-baron-cohen-1234817215/ |last=Rubin |first=Rebecca |magazine=Variety |date=2020-10-28 |access-date=2020-10-28 |title=''Borat 2'' Babysitter Doesn't Feel Betrayed by Sacha Baron Cohen, but Wishes She Were Paid More |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028234446/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/borat-2-babysitter-sacha-baron-cohen-1234817215/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。被问到3600美元的片酬是否公平时，琼斯表示：“我不能说这很公平，因为他们知道这将是一部电影，但我不知道。”琼斯的牧师称赞她是影片的“道德指南针”，考虑到她在2019冠状病毒病疫情中失业，便在[[GoFundMe|GoFundMe]]为她发起众筹活动，筹款金额三天就突破5万美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thewrap.com/borat-babysitter-jeanise-jones-duped-sacha-baron-cohen/ |title=''Borat'' Sequel Fans Raise $50,000 for Unemployed Babysitter Duped in Sacha Baron Cohen Film |date=2020-10-28 |access-date=2020-10-28 |last=Welk |first=Brian |website=TheWrap |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028230805/https://www.thewrap.com/borat-babysitter-jeanise-jones-duped-sacha-baron-cohen/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，一周内突破15万美元<ref>{{Cite web |publisher=Consequence of Sound |date=2020-10-28 |access-date=2020-10-28 |title=Fundraiser for ''Borat 2'' Babysitter Raises Over $115,000 |last=Kaye |first=Ben |url=https://consequenceofsound.net/2020/10/borat-2-babysitter-fundraiser/ |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101013754/https://consequenceofsound.net/2020/10/borat-2-babysitter-fundraiser/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |publisher=KFOR-TV |date=2020-10-30 |access-date=2020-10-31 |title=Oklahoma City Woman, Church, Receive Hundreds of Thousands in Donations After She Unknowingly Played Part in New ''Borat'' Film |last=Daniels |first=Lauren |url=https://kfor.com/news/local/oklahoma-city-woman-church-receive-hundreds-of-thousands-in-donations-after-she-unknowingly-played-part-in-new-borat-film/ |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107133414/https://kfor.com/news/local/oklahoma-city-woman-church-receive-hundreds-of-thousands-in-donations-after-she-unknowingly-played-part-in-new-borat-film/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。科恩为琼斯所在的[[俄克拉荷马城|俄克拉荷马城]]社区捐赠10万美元，款项受她的教会收取<ref name="donate">{{Cite web |url=https://people.com/movies/sacha-baron-cohen-makes-100000-donation-to-heart-of-borat-2-jeanise-jones-community/ |work=People |date=2020-10-29 |access-date=2020-10-29 |last=Russian |first=Ale |title=Sacha Baron Cohen Makes $100,000 Donation to ''Borat 2'' Babysitter Jeanise Jones' Community |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031072154/https://people.com/movies/sacha-baron-cohen-makes-100000-donation-to-heart-of-borat-2-jeanise-jones-community/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。后来，琼斯因为在电影的表现，在一部喜剧片中扮演天使<ref>{{Cite web |last=Johnston |first=Rich |title=''Borat 2''{{'}}s Jeanise Jones Is to Play an Angel in New Comedy Movie |publisher=Bleeding Cool |date=2020-11-02 |access-date=2020-11-03 |url=https://bleedingcool.com/movies/borat-2s-jeanise-jones-is-to-play-an-angel-in-new-comedy-movie/ |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102110413/https://bleedingcool.com/movies/borat-2s-jeanise-jones-is-to-play-an-angel-in-new-comedy-movie/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年1月，玛丽亚·巴卡洛娃表示她仍和琼斯保持联络<ref>{{cite web |title=Borat actress Maria Bakalova still keeps in touch with ‘true angel’ on-screen babysitter |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/maria-bakalova-borat-2-jeanise-jones-b1782319.html |website=The Independent |accessdate=2021-04-22 |date=2021-01-05 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113231331/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/maria-bakalova-borat-2-jeanise-jones-b1782319.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 种族主义指控 ===
波拉特一角在哈萨克斯坦引起巨大争议<ref name="really">{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20161028-what-kazakhstan-really-thought-of-borat |work=BBC News |date=2016-10-28 |access-date=2020-10-23 |last=Askarbekov |first=Yerlan |title=What Kazakhstan Really Thought of Borat |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021190830/https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20161028-what-kazakhstan-really-thought-of-borat |dead-url=no }}</ref>，原版电影在该国曾被封杀过一段时间，巴隆·科恩的网站也被封锁。续集上映前夕，哈萨克斯坦民众在Twitter发起#CancelBorat（取消《波拉特》）[[主题标签|主题标签]]<ref>{{Cite magazine |url=https://www.newsweek.com/borat-2-kazakhstan-reaction-sacha-baron-cohen-1541600 |title=''Borat 2'': How Kazakhstan Has Reacted to the Character |last=Spencer |first=Samuel |date=2020-10-23 |access-date=2020-10-23 |magazine=Newsweek |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023194435/https://www.newsweek.com/borat-2-kazakhstan-reaction-sacha-baron-cohen-1541600 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。敦促影片取消发行的线上请愿活动也突破10万的联署门槛。影片首映当天，美国驻[[阿拉木图|阿拉木图]]大使馆有少量民众抗议<ref>{{Cite web |publisher=Radio Free Europe |url=https://www.rferl.org/a/new-borat-film-offends-but-will-more-kazakhs-get-the-joke-this-time-/30908753.html |title=New Borat Film Offends, But Will More Kazakhs Get the Joke This Time? |last=Heil |first=Andy |date=2020-10-23 |access-date=2020-10-23 |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023154905/https://www.rferl.org/a/new-borat-film-offends-but-will-more-kazakhs-get-the-joke-this-time-/30908753.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。哈萨克斯坦和西方国家的民众都再度批评波拉特随意嘲笑哈萨克斯坦人的口音，塑造刻板印象，让哈萨克斯坦人更加被边缘化，以此假借喜剧的名义“捣蛋”<ref>{{Cite web |publisher=CNN |date=2020-10-24 |access-date=2020-10-24 |last=Tensley |first=Brandon |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/10/24/politics/borat-kazakhstan-sacha-baron-cohen-trnd/index.html |title=Reassessing the Racial Stereotyping in ''Borat'' |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024215036/https://www.cnn.com/2020/10/24/politics/borat-kazakhstan-sacha-baron-cohen-trnd/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在美哈萨克人协会（Kazakh American Association）发表声明，指影片宣扬“种族主义、文化挪用及排外情绪”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thewrap.com/borat-sequel-promotes-racism-cultural-appropriation-and-xenophobia-kazakh-american-association-says/ |title=''Borat'' Sequel Promotes 'Racism, Cultural Appropriation and Xenophobia,' Kazakh American Association Says |date=2020-10-26 |access-date=2020-10-26 |last=Welk |first=Brian |website=TheWrap |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027020429/https://www.thewrap.com/borat-sequel-promotes-racism-cultural-appropriation-and-xenophobia-kazakh-american-association-says/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[影獎季|影獎季]]前夕，该协会再度发表公开信，敦促活动主办方不要考虑这部电影<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/borat-sequel-kazakh-community-award-ban-1234833223/ |last=Oganesyan |first=Natalie |date=2020-11-15 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=Variety |title=Kazakh Organization Asks Award Shows to Disqualify ''Borat'' Sequel |archive-date=2020-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201226213215/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/borat-sequel-kazakh-community-award-ban-1234833223/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。波拉特这个角色也营造出对哈萨克斯坦的误解。尽管如此，哈国旅行社哈萨克旅游还是利用影片造成的国际影响力，将标语改成波拉特的口头禅“哈萨克斯坦，棒极了！”（Kazakhstan. Very Nice!），发布大量有影片镜头的宣传片<ref>{{Cite news |last=Stein |first=Joel |date=2020-10-26 |access-date=2020-10-26 |title=Kazakhstan, Reversing Itself, Embraces 'Borat' as Very Nice |newspaper=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/26/business/kazakhstan-embraces-borat.html |issn=0362-4331 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026140049/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/26/business/kazakhstan-embraces-borat.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

另外，[[英国国民信托|英国国民信托]]谴责影片亵渎[[塞那阿巴斯巨人像|塞那阿巴斯巨人像]]；巴黎穆斯林批评波拉特在宣传海报中接近全裸，在手上明显地戴着刻有“[[安拉|安拉]]”字样的戒指<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/muslims-demand-borat-posters-are-stripped-from-paris-buses-h8xdbfvdf |title=Muslims Want Borat Posters Stripped from Paris Buses |work=The Times |last=Bremmer |first=Charles |date=2020-11-04 |access-date=2020-11-10 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109151109/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/muslims-demand-borat-posters-are-stripped-from-paris-buses-h8xdbfvdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，后来戒指被去除<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.yahoo.com/borat-poster-paris-buses-muslim-093735359.html |title=''Borat 2'' Posters Removed from Paris Buses Amid Backlash from Muslim Community |last=Beasley |first=Tom |date=2020-11-06 |access-date=2020-11-10 |publisher=Yahoo! News |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107053055/https://news.yahoo.com/borat-poster-paris-buses-muslim-093735359.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

